(1, , , , , , , , '<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="3">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="100%" valign="top">\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="24" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Posting Buying Leads and Products</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">post_buy_help_atrdstppo </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 4px;" height="19" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Sign in at My AlibabaScript ;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Click "Post a New Buying Lead"in the"Buying Tools" section;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Complete the form, in the "My Contact Preference" section, please select "Allow all members to contact me by email only while concealing my other contact details."</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Click "Post Now" to submit.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">If you are a member, you can post buying leads under Buying Tools within My AlibabaScript, or from many other pages by clicking on the"Post Buying Leads" link in the "Buying Tools" box.\r\n<p>If you are not yet a member, you can post buying leads from many pages by clicking on the"Post Buying Leads" link in the"Buying Tools"box. Completing the following registration form, you will be registered as a free member with AlibabaScript.com.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><img title="img_postsupp" src="images/img_postsupp.JPG" alt="img_postsupp" width="504" height="215" /></p>\r\n</span> \r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="3">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Upon publication, sellers will be able to view your Trade Leads and respond accordingly. All of the sellers'' responsive messages will be sent to your own &nbsp;<a href="message_center_help.php">Message Center</a> in<a href="mypage.php">My Page</a></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Upon publication, buyers will be able to see your Products and Selling Leads, to which they can reply. All of the buyers'' messages will be sent to your own Message Center in My Page.</span>\r\n<div><img src="../images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="5" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Related Topics:</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top"><a href="selling_tools.php">Detailed Steps to Post a Product</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top"><a href="message_center_help.php">Message Center</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top">&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<span style="font-size: 12px;"> </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="3">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="100%" valign="top">\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="24" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Posting a Selling Leads </strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" height="19" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<span style="font-size: 14px;">\r\n<li><span style="font-size: small;"><a href="../selling_tools.php?sid=sTab4#top">Posting a Product</a></span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: small;"><a href="../selling_tools.php?sid=sTab4#manage">Managing my Products</a></span></li>\r\n<span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong> </strong></span></span> \r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="top" height="24" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Posting a Product </strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="46" valign="top">\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;">Go to "Selling Tools" in My Page and click "Post New Product." When you get to the "Post New Product" page, provide the required information and click "Submit" when finished.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Product Name:</strong></span> <span style="font-size: 12px;">Please enter an appropriate product name here, not a model number, or a company name, or a brand name.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top">\r\n<div id="paddedbox"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Product Photo:</strong></span><br /> <ol><span style="font-size: 12px;">\r\n<li>Size: less than 200K.</li>\r\n<li>Format: JPG</li>\r\n<li>The name of your product picture should be in English.</li>\r\n</span></ol></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" align="left" valign="top">\r\n<div id="div">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Keywords:</strong></span><span style="font-size: 12px;">Keyword means the word that your company/product/Trade Lead is searched with. Four out of five customers will search for what they need directly. Keyword is at the heart of searching because if your keyword is matched with a customer''s sought products, your Trade Leads or products can be listed for buyers instantly.</span></div>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;">Selecting Proper Keywords<br /> Example: <br /> Subject: Buy Green Fuji Apple<br /> Category: Agriculture/Fruit<br /> </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong> Three Key Words:</strong></span> <br /> <span style="font-size: 12px;"> No: Green, Fuji, apple</span><br /> <span style="font-size: 12px;">Yes: Green Fuji Apple, Fuji Apple, Fruit </span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;">Apple is a real product, and apple is a kind of fruit, so "apple" and "fruit" can be keywords. Green (color) and Fuji (place of origin or species) are adjectives, meaning they modify "apple." They can not be keywords. Nobody searching with such adjectives will find products.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top">\r\n<div id="div2">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Category:</strong></span> <span style="font-size: 12px;">Try to select the most relevant category. If possible, do not select "other." More than one third of buyers look for products by category. A precise category listing will enhance your chances of being found easily.</span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><img title="img_sellproductpho" src="images/img_sellproductpho.jpg" alt="img_sellproductpho" width="504" height="202" /></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br /></span></div>\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><img title="img_sellproductdes" src="images/img_sellproductdes.jpg" alt="img_sellproductdes" width="504" height="202" /></span></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="3">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Product Description:</strong></span><span style="font-size: 12px;">Make sure your description refers only to the features of the product in the picture, not all of your products or your company''s general information. Please note: Brief Description will be displayed on the search result list page.</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" align="left">\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;">You will receive a message telling you your product(s) have been submitted to our editing team. Products, upon approval, are published on 2daybiz.com within 24 hours. Once your products are approved, you can choose to display them or not display them. The "Manage Products" table is where you can manage which products you wish to display.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;">If your products are not approved (i.e., you are required to submit more information), the status will be shown on your My <span style="font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">2daybiz&nbsp;</span>homepage in the "Requires Editing" section with "Return Reason".</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Please note:</strong></span><span style="font-size: 12px;"> The approval process applies to all postings on <span style="font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">2daybiz</span>.com, including, Company Profile, products, buying leads and selling leads.</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="manage" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong>Managing my Products</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;">To edit your products, go to My <span style="font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">2daybiz</span>. In the "Manage Products" section, you can view all of your products'' status at any time. They are classified under three sections:</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" height="19" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<span style="font-size: 12px;">\r\n<li>"Editing Required" includes products that have been rejected by <span style="font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">2daybiz</span>.com because they require editing.</li>\r\n<li>"Approval Pending" includes products that have been posted but have yet to be approved. The approval process usually takes 24 hours.</li>\r\n<li>"Approved" includes those products that are on display and those not on display. You can choose which products you wish to display.</li>\r\n</span> \r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top">\r\n<div><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Please note:</strong></span><span style="font-size: 12px;">You may edit or delete only products currently located in the "Editing Required" and "Approved" sections.</span></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<table style="width: 100%;" border="0" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="3">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="text-align: left;">\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" width="100%" height="24" align="center" valign="middle">\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#msgcen">What is Message Center?</a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#reply">How do I Send and reply to Messages? </a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#unlimit">Storing Unlimited Messages in the Message Center? </a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#cont">What is Contact List? </a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#managcont">How do I Manage Contacts?</a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#search">What is Search?</a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#bulk">What is Bulk Folder?</a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#use">How do I use my block list?</a></li>\r\n<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="message_center_help.php?sid=sTab4#receive">How Can I receive My lost Messages?</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="msgcen" height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>What is Message Center?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Message Center is a communication management tool that gives you an easy and efficient way to track the messages you send and receive from other lowermarket.com members. The benefits include:</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" height="19" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">The ability to conveniently manage your <span style="font-size: 12px;">Lowermarket.com</span> Inquiries and Quotations.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">A central location in which to store all of your messages.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 12px;">Aggressive spam-filtering tools.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="reply" height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>How do I Send and reply to Messages?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="19" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">You can either send messages to your intended party by clicking the "Contact Now" button in the product page, or by directly clicking the "Send Message" button in Message Center.\r\n<p>You can check your sent messages and replies in Message Center.</p>\r\n<p>You may take the following steps to send and reply to messages:</p>\r\n</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" height="66" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<span style="font-size: 12px;">\r\n<li>Browse or search for your interested product.</li>\r\n<li>Click "Contact Now" and send messages.</li>\r\n<li>Check replies in Message Center and reply accordingly.</li>\r\n</span> \r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="unlimit" height="24" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>Storing Unlimited Messages in the Message Center?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="24" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Your Message Center Inbox can hold unlimited messages. Messages from the last 90 days are listed in your Inbox, while all prior messages are stored chronologically and can be accessed by using the drop-down menu on the tool-bar. Messages from the previous two years will be deleted automatically.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="cont" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>What is Contact List?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="31" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Your contact list is your list of people and companies with whom you correspond through lowermarket.com. It contains contact and other detailed information for your business use.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="managcont" height="29" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">How do I Manage Contacts?</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">To manage your contacts, you can:<br /> </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<span style="font-size: 12px;">\r\n<li>Add <span style="font-size: 12px;">lowermarket.com</span> members or non-members to your contact list.</li>\r\n<li>Create groups for better management.</li>\r\n<li>Check and edit your contacts'' information.</li>\r\n</span> \r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="29" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">Please note that your contacts in Message Center are integrated into your TradeManager contact list.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="search" height="29" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>What is Search?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td height="29" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">In Message Center, you can search messages by sender/receiver name, subject, message details, company name, phone number and fax number. For example, if you search "ABC," all messages containing "ABC" will be flagged.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="bulk" height="29" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>What is Bulk Folder?</strong> </span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" height="19" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">The bulk folder is the folder in the Message Center of My <span style="font-size: 12px;">2daybiz&nbsp;</span>that houses suspected junk mail/spam. Messages may be recovered by clicking "Not Spam." These suspected junk mail/spam messages will be stored here for two months, after which they will be deleted.</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="use" colspan="2" height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>How do I use my block list?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" height="19" align="left" valign="top"><br /><span style="font-size: 12px;"> Sometimes members receive unwanted correspondence. You can use "Block List" in Message Center to filter out unwanted messages. With this control method, messages from Member IDs, email addresses or countries you wish to block will be deleted automatically.\r\n<p>With "Block List" you can add new blocking details or remove existing blocks by taking the following steps:</p>\r\n</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="padding-left: 20px;" colspan="2" height="19" valign="top">\r\n<ul>\r\n<span style="font-size: 12px;">\r\n<li>Sign in with your registered email address and password at http://www.<span style="font-size: 12px;">lowermarket.com</span>/mypage.</li>\r\n<li>Click "Block List" in Message Center.</li>\r\n<li> Complete the form.</li>\r\n<li>Click "Block" to confirm your blocked settings.</li>\r\n</span> \r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td id="receive" colspan="2" height="19" align="left" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><strong>How Can I receive My lost Messages?</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan="2" height="19" valign="top"><span style="font-size: 12px;">\r\n<p>If you are an <span style="font-size: 12px;">lowermarket </span>member, you can sign in to Message Center with your Member ID and password, where you can check and reply to your messages.</p>\r\n<p>If you encounter any problem retrieving a lost message, please contact our service team.</p>\r\n</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">ClassifLied</strong>&nbsp;is a platform...Where classified flies..!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">We are a global marketplace with extensive inventory of buying and selling businesses that suit a range to investors or buyers.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">We offers online classifieds with our advanced freemium listing model, to provide a simple solution to the complications involved in Selling, Buying, Trading, Discussing, Organizing and Meeting people near you.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;">Classiflied cares for Recapitalization, Acquisition, and ROI as per your business needs.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Our Aim:&nbsp;</strong>To use and leverage the unique qualities of the products and expand the customer''s network with maximum of growing opportunity.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Our Motive:&nbsp;</strong>To support full with proper plan, execution attract, engage and to set perfect alignment between buyer, seller, agents and administrator.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: small;"><strong style="font-weight: bold;">Our Activities:&nbsp;</strong>Designed in a way to result with a profit towards online marketplace.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '');
